{"type":"info-page","slug":"vir/content/early/2013/01/29/vir.0.049759-0.short","journal":"vir","canonical":"https://www.sgmjournals.org/vir/content/early/2013/01/29/vir.0.049759-0.short","title":"Journal of General Virology","bodyHtml":"<div class=\"article abstract-view\">\n\n        <h1 id=\"article-title-1\">Coronaviruses in bats from Mexico</h1>\n        <div class=\"contributors\">\n          <ol class=\"contributor-list\" id=\"contrib-group-1\">\n            <li class=\"contributor\" id=\"contrib-1\">\n              <span class=\"name\"><a class=\"name-search\" href=\"/vir/search?author1=Simon+Anthony&amp;sortspec=date&amp;submit=Submit\">Simon Anthony</a></span><a id=\"xref-aff-1-1\" class=\"xref-aff\" href=\"#aff-1\">1</a><span class=\"xref-sep\">,</span><a id=\"xref-corresp-1-1\" class=\"xref-fn\" href=\"#corresp-1\">7</a>,\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"contributor\" id=\"contrib-2\">\n              <span class=\"name\"><a class=\"name-search\" href=\"/vir/search?author1=Rafael+Ojeda-Flores&amp;sortspec=date&amp;submit=Submit\">Rafael Ojeda-Flores</a></span><a id=\"xref-aff-2-1\" class=\"xref-aff\" href=\"#aff-2\">2</a>,\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"contributor\" id=\"contrib-3\">\n              <span class=\"name\"><a class=\"name-search\" href=\"/vir/search?author1=Oscar+Rico-Ch%C3%A1vez&amp;sortspec=date&amp;submit=Submit\">Oscar Rico-Chávez</a></span><a id=\"xref-aff-2-2\" class=\"xref-aff\" href=\"#aff-2\">2</a>,\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"contributor\" id=\"contrib-4\">\n              <span class=\"name\"><a class=\"name-search\" href=\"/vir/search?author1=Isamara+Navarrete-Macias&amp;sortspec=date&amp;submit=Submit\">Isamara Navarrete-Macias</a></span><a id=\"xref-aff-1-2\" class=\"xref-aff\" href=\"#aff-1\">1</a>,\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"contributor\" id=\"contrib-5\">\n              <span class=\"name\"><a class=\"name-search\" href=\"/vir/search?author1=Carlos+Zambrana-Torrelio&amp;sortspec=date&amp;submit=Submit\">Carlos Zambrana-Torrelio</a></span><a id=\"xref-aff-3-1\" class=\"xref-aff\" href=\"#aff-3\">3</a>,\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"contributor\" id=\"contrib-6\">\n              <span class=\"name\"><a class=\"name-search\" href=\"/vir/search?author1=Melinda+K.+Rostal&amp;sortspec=date&amp;submit=Submit\">Melinda K. Rostal</a></span><a id=\"xref-aff-3-2\" class=\"xref-aff\" href=\"#aff-3\">3</a>,\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"contributor\" id=\"contrib-7\">\n              <span class=\"name\"><a class=\"name-search\" href=\"/vir/search?author1=Jonathan+H.+Epstein&amp;sortspec=date&amp;submit=Submit\">Jonathan H. Epstein</a></span><a id=\"xref-aff-3-3\" class=\"xref-aff\" href=\"#aff-3\">3</a>,\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"contributor\" id=\"contrib-8\">\n              <span class=\"name\"><a class=\"name-search\" href=\"/vir/search?author1=Teresita+Tipps&amp;sortspec=date&amp;submit=Submit\">Teresita Tipps</a></span><a id=\"xref-aff-4-1\" class=\"xref-aff\" href=\"#aff-4\">4</a>,\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"contributor\" id=\"contrib-9\">\n              <span class=\"name\"><a class=\"name-search\" href=\"/vir/search?author1=Eliza+Liang&amp;sortspec=date&amp;submit=Submit\">Eliza Liang</a></span><a id=\"xref-aff-3-4\" class=\"xref-aff\" href=\"#aff-3\">3</a>,\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"contributor\" id=\"contrib-10\">\n              <span class=\"name\"><a class=\"name-search\" href=\"/vir/search?author1=Maria+Sanchez-Leon&amp;sortspec=date&amp;submit=Submit\">Maria Sanchez-Leon</a></span><a id=\"xref-aff-1-3\" class=\"xref-aff\" href=\"#aff-1\">1</a>,\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"contributor\" id=\"contrib-11\">\n              <span class=\"name\"><a class=\"name-search\" href=\"/vir/search?author1=J.+Sotomayor-Bonilla&amp;sortspec=date&amp;submit=Submit\">J. Sotomayor-Bonilla</a></span><a id=\"xref-aff-2-3\" class=\"xref-aff\" href=\"#aff-2\">2</a>,\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"contributor\" id=\"contrib-12\">\n              <span class=\"name\"><a class=\"name-search\" href=\"/vir/search?author1=A.+Alonso+Aguirre&amp;sortspec=date&amp;submit=Submit\">A. Alonso Aguirre</a></span><a id=\"xref-aff-5-1\" class=\"xref-aff\" href=\"#aff-5\">5</a>,\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"contributor\" id=\"contrib-13\">\n              <span class=\"name\"><a class=\"name-search\" href=\"/vir/search?author1=R.+%C3%81vila&amp;sortspec=date&amp;submit=Submit\">R. Ávila</a></span><a id=\"xref-aff-2-4\" class=\"xref-aff\" href=\"#aff-2\">2</a>,\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"contributor\" id=\"contrib-14\">\n              <span class=\"name\"><a class=\"name-search\" href=\"/vir/search?author1=Rodrigo+A.+Medell%C3%ADn&amp;sortspec=date&amp;submit=Submit\">Rodrigo A. Medellín</a></span><a id=\"xref-aff-2-5\" class=\"xref-aff\" href=\"#aff-2\">2</a>,\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"contributor\" id=\"contrib-15\">\n              <span class=\"name\"><a class=\"name-search\" href=\"/vir/search?author1=Tracey+Goldstein&amp;sortspec=date&amp;submit=Submit\">Tracey Goldstein</a></span><a id=\"xref-aff-6-1\" class=\"xref-aff\" href=\"#aff-6\">6</a>,\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"contributor\" id=\"contrib-16\">\n              <span class=\"name\"><a class=\"name-search\" href=\"/vir/search?author1=Gerardo+Suz%C3%A1n&amp;sortspec=date&amp;submit=Submit\">Gerardo Suzán</a></span><a id=\"xref-aff-2-6\" class=\"xref-aff\" href=\"#aff-2\">2</a>,\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"contributor\" id=\"contrib-17\">\n              <span class=\"name\"><a class=\"name-search\" href=\"/vir/search?author1=Peter+Daszak&amp;sortspec=date&amp;submit=Submit\">Peter Daszak</a></span><a id=\"xref-aff-3-5\" class=\"xref-aff\" href=\"#aff-3\">3</a> and\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"last\" id=\"contrib-18\">\n              <span class=\"name\"><a class=\"name-search\" href=\"/vir/search?author1=W.+Ian+Lipkin&amp;sortspec=date&amp;submit=Submit\">W. Ian Lipkin</a></span><a id=\"xref-aff-1-4\" class=\"xref-aff\" href=\"#aff-1\">1</a>\n            </li>\n          </ol>\n          <ol class=\"affiliation-list\">\n            <li class=\"aff\">\n              <a id=\"aff-1\" name=\"aff-1\"></a>\n              <address>\n                <sup>1</sup> Columbia University;\n              </address>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"aff\">\n              <a id=\"aff-2\" name=\"aff-2\"></a>\n              <address>\n                <sup>2</sup> Universidad Nacional Autonoma de Mexico;\n              </address>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"aff\">\n              <a id=\"aff-3\" name=\"aff-3\"></a>\n              <address>\n                <sup>3</sup> EcoHealth Alliance;\n              </address>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"aff\">\n              <a id=\"aff-4\" name=\"aff-4\"></a>\n              <address>\n                <sup>4</sup> Angelo State University;\n              </address>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"aff\">\n              <a id=\"aff-5\" name=\"aff-5\"></a>\n              <address>\n                <sup>5</sup> George Mason University;\n              </address>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"aff\">\n              <a id=\"aff-6\" name=\"aff-6\"></a>\n              <address>\n                <sup>6</sup> UC Davis\n              </address>\n            </li>\n          </ol>\n          <ol class=\"corresp-list\">\n            <li class=\"corresp\" id=\"corresp-1\">\n              <a class=\"rev-xref\" href=\"#xref-corresp-1-1\">↵</a><sup>7</sup> E-mail: <span class=\"em-link\"><span class=\"em-addr\">sja2127{at}columbia.edu</span></span>\n            </li>\n          </ol>\n\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"section abstract\" id=\"abstract-1\">\n          <h2>Abstract</h2>\n          <p id=\"p-1\">Bats are reservoirs for a wide range of human pathogens including Nipah, Hendra , rabies, Ebola, Marburg and SARS coronavirus. The recent implication of a novel β-coronavirus (CoV) as the cause of fatal respiratory disease in the Middle East emphasizes the importance of surveillance for CoVs that have potential to move from bats into the human population. In a screen of 606 bats from 42 different species in Campeche, Chiapas and Mexico City we identified 13 distinct CoVs. Nine were α-CoVs; four were β –CoVs. Twelve were novel. Analyses of these viruses in the context of their hosts and ecological habitat indicated that host species is a strong selective driver in CoV evolution, even in allopatric populations separated by significant geographical distance; and that a single species/genus of bat can contain multiple CoVs. A β –CoV with 96.5% amino acid identity to the β –CoV associated with human disease in the Middle East was found in a Nyctinomops laticaudatus bat, suggesting that efforts to identify the viral reservoir should include surveillance of the families Molossidae/Vespertilionidae, or the closely related Nycteridae/Emballonuridae. While it is important to investigate unknown viral diversity in bats, it is also important to remember that the majority of viruses they carry will not pose any clinical risk, and bats should not be ubiquitously stigmatized as significant threats to public health.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"social-bookmarking\">\n        <ul class=\"social-bookmark-links\">\n          <li class=\"social-bookmarking-item social-bookmarking-item-citeulike\">\n            <a href=\"/vir/external-ref?tag_url=http://vir.sgmjournals.org/cgi/content/long/vir.0.049759-0v1&amp;title=Coronaviruses%20in%20bats%20from%20Mexico+--+Anthony%20et%20al.+--+VIR&amp;doi=10.1099/vir.0.049759-0&amp;link_type=CITEULIKE\"><img src=\"/shared/img/common/social-bookmarking/citeulike.gif\" alt=\"Add to CiteULike\" title=\"CiteULike\"></a><span class=\"soc-bm-link-text\">CiteULike</span>\n          </